<p>Youâ€™re on a game show and they show you three doors (theyâ€™re all shut). They tell you behind two of these doors are goats, and behind one of them is a brand new car! They say you get to pick one door, then theyâ€™ll open up one of the remaining doors to reveal a goat, then ask you if you want to change your choice. What do you say?</p>

<p>What you know:</p>

